  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1804890/extras/99fb8f4b0489a1b6723a4490bfa2fd32.avif?t=1745506717\" width=600 height=120 /></span><br><br>Take control of your seeker and become the space miner you always wanted to be.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1804890/extras/85bbd4213b2396fd0feaa023173c18b2.poster.avif?t=1745506717\" width=600 height=120 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1804890/extras/85bbd4213b2396fd0feaa023173c18b2.webm?t=1745506717\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br>Turn grid squares to destroy enemy drones before they destroy you.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1804890/extras/fdf7f193ca1cc90460b7009fff52f2b5.poster.avif?t=1745506717\" width=600 height=119 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1804890/extras/fdf7f193ca1cc90460b7009fff52f2b5.webm?t=1745506717\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Space-themed puzzles with real-time-strategy elements<br></li><li>2-hour-long single-player campaign<br></li><li>Endless Mode: Play generated levels with seed numbers and unlockables<br></li><li>Challenge Mode: Try to beat remixed campaign levels<br></li><li>Level Editor: Create and upload your own levels from within the game<br></li><li>Player Levels: Download and play levels created by other players<br></li><li>Chill soundtrack by Muddasheep featuring KAON and Veven<br></li><li>Character art by Elhyana Guillaume</li></ul><br>(Uploading and downloading player levels requires an internet connection.)<br><br>ℹ This game has been released as \"Turn to Mine\" on all major consoles.",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1804890/extras/99fb8f4b0489a1b6723a4490bfa2fd32.avif?t=1745506717\" width=600 height=120 /></span><br><br>Take control of your seeker and become the space miner you always wanted to be.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1804890/extras/85bbd4213b2396fd0feaa023173c18b2.poster.avif?t=1745506717\" width=600 height=120 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1804890/extras/85bbd4213b2396fd0feaa023173c18b2.webm?t=1745506717\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br>Turn grid squares to destroy enemy drones before they destroy you.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1804890/extras/fdf7f193ca1cc90460b7009fff52f2b5.poster.avif?t=1745506717\" width=600 height=119 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1804890/extras/fdf7f193ca1cc90460b7009fff52f2b5.webm?t=1745506717\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Space-themed puzzles with real-time-strategy elements<br></li><li>2-hour-long single-player campaign<br></li><li>Endless Mode: Play generated levels with seed numbers and unlockables<br></li><li>Challenge Mode: Try to beat remixed campaign levels<br></li><li>Level Editor: Create and upload your own levels from within the game<br></li><li>Player Levels: Download and play levels created by other players<br></li><li>Chill soundtrack by Muddasheep featuring KAON and Veven<br></li><li>Character art by Elhyana Guillaume</li></ul><br>(Uploading and downloading player levels requires an internet